{"scenicName": "咸宁", "city": "咸宁", "scenes": [{"text": "大家好呀！我是红美铃，红魔馆的门卫，今天带大家去一个特别的地方——湖北咸宁！", "expression": "confident", "audioFile": "seg-00.mp3", "durationInFrames": 209, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "咸宁可是被誉为“桂花之乡”和“温泉之城”呢，这两个名号可不是吹出来的哦~", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-01.mp3", "durationInFrames": 192, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "它位于湖北省东南部，幕阜山脉北麓，坐拥长江中游的温润气候，别提多舒服啦！", "expression": "default", "audioFile": "seg-02.mp3", "durationInFrames": 169, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "全市面积约9861平方公里，地势南高北低，森林覆盖率超过40%，空气好得让人嫉妒呀！", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-03.mp3", "durationInFrames": 182, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "说到历史，咸宁可是三国文化的重镇，赤壁之战的主战场就在它辖下的赤壁市！", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-04.mp3", "durationInFrames": 216, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "当年周瑜一把火，烧得曹操丢盔弃甲，现在去赤壁古战场还能看到摩崖石刻“赤壁”二字呢。", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-05.mp3", "durationInFrames": 204, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "另外，明末李自成在通山县九宫山殉难，这地方也藏着一段悲壮的传奇故事哦。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-06.mp3", "durationInFrames": 235, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "咱们先看核心亮点——温泉！咸宁的温泉水质纯净，富含多种矿物质，泡一泡浑身轻松。", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-07.mp3", "durationInFrames": 212, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "碧桂园温泉、三江温泉、温泉谷……随便一家都有几十个泡池，山野风光配热气腾腾的泉水，绝了！", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-08.mp3", "durationInFrames": 196, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "接着是桂花，咸宁有2000多年桂花栽培史，每到秋天，满城金桂银桂飘香，简直像掉进蜜罐里。", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-09.mp3", "durationInFrames": 222, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "桂花源景区里还有一棵千年古桂树，树干要几个人才能合抱，许愿特别灵验哦~", "expression": "surprised", "audioFile": "seg-10.mp3", "durationInFrames": 179, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "九宫山也不能错过！主峰老鸦尖海拔1657米，夏季平均气温才22℃，是华中避暑胜地。", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-11.mp3", "durationInFrames": 184, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "山上的云中湖像一面镜子嵌在山巅，运气好还能看到云海佛光，美得像仙境。", "expression": "excited", "audioFile": "seg-12.mp3", "durationInFrames": 171, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "还有刘家桥村，这座明清古村落有400多年历史，小桥流水，青石板路，拍照打卡超有感觉。", "expression": "happy3", "audioFile": "seg-13.mp3", "durationInFrames": 166, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "咸宁的文化价值也特别深厚——三国古战场遗址、桂花诗词文化、还有温泉养生哲学，都值得细细品味。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-14.mp3", "durationInFrames": 175, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "这里的温泉文化可以追溯到唐宋，文人墨客留下的诗篇多达上百首，泡着温泉读古诗，雅致吧？", "expression": "happy_confident", "audioFile": "seg-15.mp3", "durationInFrames": 162, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "桂花更是融入了当地人生活，桂花糕、桂花酒、桂花茶，香甜得让人舍不得走。", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-16.mp3", "durationInFrames": 178, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "旅行贴士来啦~最佳季节是秋季（9-11月）赏桂花，或者冬季（12-2月）泡温泉，各有风味。", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-17.mp3", "durationInFrames": 196, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "建议花三天时间：一天泡温泉逛市区，一天游赤壁古战场，一天爬九宫山，节奏刚刚好。", "expression": "thinking", "audioFile": "seg-18.mp3", "durationInFrames": 178, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "注意啦：部分温泉高峰期人多，最好提前订票，赤壁古战场面积大，穿双舒服的鞋子哦。", "expression": "default", "audioFile": "seg-19.mp3", "durationInFrames": 167, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "好啦，咸宁的故事说不完，这座既有历史厚度又有生活温度的城市，绝对值得你亲自来体验！", "expression": "confident", "audioFile": "seg-20.mp3", "durationInFrames": 168, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}, {"text": "我是红美铃，期待在温泉热气里与大家偶遇，咱们下个景区再见啦~拜拜！", "expression": "happy5", "audioFile": "seg-21.mp3", "durationInFrames": 164, "imageFile": "vid_bd0a2b3e39dc-img-00.jpg"}], "totalFrames": 4215}